During the period, e-filing support will be offered through an online platform running every weekday from 10am to noon and from 2pm to 4pm. Acting Chief Justice Philomena Mwilu has closed courts, tribunals and all registries in the five counties that President Uhuru Kenyatta declared Covid-19 infested. 



